       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. DC-GATEWAY-EVENT-FROM-JSON.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-PATH PIC X(128).
       01 WS-NUMBER PIC S9(18) COMP-5.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 DC-GATEWAY-JSON PIC X(8192).
       COPY "discord-event.cpy".
       COPY "discord-result.cpy".

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING
           DC-GATEWAY-JSON
           DC-EVENT
           DC-RESULT.
       MAIN.
           INITIALIZE DC-EVENT
           MOVE "$.t" TO WS-PATH
           CALL "DC-JSON-GET-STRING"
               USING DC-GATEWAY-JSON WS-PATH DC-EVENT-NAME DC-RESULT
           IF DC-STATUS-CODE NOT = DC-STATUS-OK
               GOBACK
           END-IF
           MOVE "$.s" TO WS-PATH
           CALL "DC-JSON-GET-NUMBER"
               USING DC-GATEWAY-JSON WS-PATH WS-NUMBER DC-RESULT
	           IF DC-STATUS-CODE = DC-STATUS-OK
	               MOVE WS-NUMBER TO DC-EVENT-SEQUENCE
	           END-IF
	           MOVE DC-GATEWAY-JSON TO DC-EVENT-PAYLOAD
	           MOVE FUNCTION LENGTH(
	               FUNCTION TRIM(DC-GATEWAY-JSON TRAILING))
	               TO DC-EVENT-PAYLOAD-LENGTH
	           CALL "DC-RESULT-OK" USING DC-RESULT
	           GOBACK.
       END PROGRAM DC-GATEWAY-EVENT-FROM-JSON.
